opentsdb
========

Jobs to run manually after running the playbook
===============================================

Create the database tables
--------------------------

Only do this once, on the first TSD that you deploy.

# su hbase
$ env COMPRESSION=LZ4 HBASE_HOME=$HBASE_PREFIX /usr/share/opentsdb/tools/create_table.sh

Ignore this message: "warning: compression codec 'LZ4' might not be supported."
Our Ansible role made LZ4 supported.


Role variables
==============

opentsdb_auto_create_metrics
----------------------------

Whether or not to automatically create UIDs for new metric types.
Defaults to false.
